<h2 id="潮流开源">潮流开源</h2>
<p><strong>pyscript：在 html 里面写 python</strong><br>
<a href="https://github.com/pyscript/pyscript">https://github.com/pyscript/pyscript</a><br>
大概这样的写法，有一定新意，可以试试他自己的 example。</p>
<pre is:raw="" class="astro-code" style="background-color: #0d1117; overflow-x: auto;"><code><span class="line"><span style="color: #C9D1D9">&#x3C;</span><span style="color: #7EE787">html</span><span style="color: #C9D1D9">></span></span>
